Freestanding industrial building located in Leduc Business Park with exposure to Airport Road, great access to Highway 2 and the Edmonton International Airport. High end, modern office space with ample windows and natural light. Low site coverage ratio of 15%. Building includes oversized grade loading doors, bridge cranes, dock loading, and windows in shop space.

Corner site providing two points of ingress/egress. Fenced, gated and graveled yard space. Lease rate starting at $10.00 per sq. ft.
